{"tid":13200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"醉男以為和女友做愛 醒來發現是男人","createTime":"2016-11-30T03:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T06:30:16.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"081943c3820793b08cbbeed40ef6c2f8bfe0e393","tid":13200,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"英國一名男子日前喝得大醉，躺在床上的時候，他一直以為是女友在和他做愛，但男子醒來後發現，與他做愛的人，是一名22歲男人伊拉德(Dale Everard)。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據英國《The Press and Journal》網站報導，男子指控，他在去年5月和女友外出玩，並認識了伊拉德，當時伊拉德說他原本有個同志約會，卻被放鴿子。伊拉德隨後和這段情侶聊了起來，大家邊聊邊喝酒，聊得很盡興。男子之後表示有點累，於是先行回家休息，女子則繼續和伊拉德聊天。之後女子邀伊拉德回家續攤，男子看到女友帶不相干的男人回來，先是和女友吵了一番，隨後男子又回到床上，倒頭大睡。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n男子因為喝得大醉，意識不太清楚，他隱約感覺有人在跟他做愛，直覺對方應該是女友，但到隔日清晨5點多醒來後，竟發現睡在他身旁的不是女友，而是伊拉德。伊拉德之後承認「是我『月工』了你」，男子也對伊拉德提起訴訟。該案在昨日開庭審理，伊拉德被註冊為性侵犯，所受刑罰將在今年稍晚判決。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"40d1fc68b1a54a85ee424d3a868dd72fd12ab53e","tid":13200,"uid":2116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"想知佢平時同女朋友玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人插緊都可以當同女朋友做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abdd7c201f405610df7a8d9e3db6cfcfaf9e433","tid":13200,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ef4ed5d8cc611d625adff3c5a79dd9389cac949","tid":13200,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:13:29.000Z","msg":"「是我『月工』了你」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b61d0dd056f79f6b0b330f4d8b05b4c19743703","tid":13200,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知佢平時同女朋友玩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人插緊都可以當同女朋友做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條女帶假鳩"},{"pid":"97c1d1c77dc97524e52ef9fd3066a663c62c85df","tid":13200,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"絕望真相是"},{"pid":"307c2505e00778f4f356b108c485df7b21b8ef9e","tid":13200,"uid":19553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絕望真相是</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事實呀"},{"pid":"ed2de20a4c9aafa49b33ffea2139d86af284fa83","tid":13200,"uid":36838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"肛佢就話姐，比人肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}